    stable 1.0Beta6 1.0Beta5 0.3.8 0.3.7
   require gtk+-v1.2 cdrtools
  optional ORBit        '' --without-orbit for COBRA support
  optional cdrdao       '' ''              disk-at-once program to burn DAO audio or data CDRs
  optional esound       '' --without-esd   for enlightenment sound mixer support
  optional gnome-libs   '' --without-gnome for gnome integration
  optional mpg321       '' ''              to read mp3 data from stdin and pipe it to stdout
  optional sox          '' ''              to convert wav-files into raw cdda format
  optional vorbis-tools '' ''              to process ogg-vorbis files
  category disk/cd
 attribute x11
    source http://gnometoaster.rulez.org/archive/gtoaster$VERSION.tgz
  homepage http://gnometoaster.rulez.org/
      desc 'gtoaster provides a cd creation suite with a gtk+ GUI.'
